<Speaker 1>Hey everyone! I am so excited to let you guys know that the Sheen Kids and Baby Showroom will be at the Melbourne Convention Exhibition Centre from July the 12th to the 13th.

<Speaker 1>Really excited.

00:20.640 --> 00:23.040
<Speaker 1>I have a whole box here to show you.

<Speaker 1>Let's get into it.

<Speaker 1>Got some cute mini bags here.

<Speaker 1>I'll open one to show you.

00:31.040 --> 00:35.160
<Speaker 1>10 pack of the kids socks in black and white with a cute little bow.

00:35.920 --> 00:39.960
<Speaker 1>4 pack of the kids stockings just under $5.

00:40.360 --> 00:42.080
<Speaker 1>Okay, I'm dying at these shoes.

<Speaker 1>Oh my god, these are so cute.

<Speaker 1>I got one each for the girls and I also got them in black.

<Speaker 1>Ohh I can't deal, they're so cute.

<Speaker 1>How cute are these bunny gloves?

<Speaker 1>We are in Melbourne and it is freezing and our fingers are going to snap, so these are perfect.

01:07.120 --> 01:08.240

<Speaker 1>They always have some really nice sets, fun.

<Speaker 1>Got these pants, these strawberry pants.

<Speaker 1>and the matching top.
